                  <provenance>The name(s) of the original donor(s) has been
                     erased in the concluding supplication formula in <locus target="#97ra">97ra</locus> and replaced with the following ones: Malkǝʾa Śǝllāse,
                     ʾAwsābǝyos, Gabra ʾAragāwi, Walda Giyorgis, ʾAqalesya, Walatta Śǝllāse.
                     The same names are written in supplication formulas, over erased name(s) of the
                     original donor(s), throughout the Ms.: ʾAqalesya (<locus target="#3vb">3vb</locus>, 77ra, 79ra, 81rab, 85ra, 87ra, 93ra, 96va), Malkǝʾa Śǝllāse
                     (<locus target="#3vb">3vb</locus>, 79rb, 80rb, 85ra, 87rb, 92vb, 93vb),
                     Walatta Śǝllāse (<locus target="#77ra">77ra</locus>, 85va), ʾAwsābǝyos (<locus target="#80rb">80rb</locus>, 82va, 85va, 91vb), 
                     Gabra ʾAragāwi (<locus target="#82va">82va</locus>), Walda Giyorgis (<locus target="#89rb">89rb</locus>, 89va, 91vb). 
 The names are written by a secondary hand
                     and rubricated in strong scarlet.</provenance>
